'''Jamshid Mahmudovich Iskanderov''' ([[Cyrillic|Uzbek Cyrillic]]: Жамшид Искандеров; born 16 October 1993) is an Uzbek professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[FC Neftchi Fergana|Neftchi Fergana]] and [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]]. He played at the [[2013 FIFA U-20 World Cup]], [[2015 AFC Asian Cup qualification]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2015-02-06 |title=Jamshid Iskanderov - Player Profile - Football - Eurosport Asia |url=http://asia.eurosport.com/football/jamshid-iskanderov_prs347417/person.shtml |access-date=2024-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206020306/http://asia.eurosport.com/football/jamshid-iskanderov_prs347417/person.shtml |archive-date=2015-02-06 }}</ref><ref>[http://espnfc.com/player/_/id/185631/jamshid-iskanderov?cc=4716 ESPNFC profile]</ref>

==Club career==

===Pakhtakor===
Iskanderov made his debut in [[Uzbek League]] on 28 May 2011 as [[FK Samarqand-Dinamo]] player in an away match against [[Qizilqum Zarafshon]], coming in as a substitute in the 57th minute.<ref>{{cite web|title=Qizilqum vs. Dinamo Samarqand 2-1|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2011/05/28/uzbekistan/pfl/qizilqum-zarafshon/dinamo-fk-samarkand/1090038/ |work=soccerway|access-date=28 May 2011}}</ref> Since 2011 he has played for Pakhtakor. In 2014, he was named twice, in May and October, as [[2014 Uzbek League#Monthly awards|Player of the Month]] in Uzbek League.

On 6 March 2015 he won the "2014 Player of the Year in Uzbek League" award.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gazeta.uz/2015/03/06/football/ |script-title=ru: Названы лучшие в сфере футбола в 2014 года| language= ru |publisher= gazeta.uz|date=2015-03-06}}</ref>

==International career==
He made his debut for [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] on 6 September 2013 in the [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification – AFC fifth round|2014 FIFA World Cup qualification]] match against [[Jordan national football team|Jordan]]. In [[2015 AFC Asian Cup]] in Australia, he appeared in three matches.

